WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.695
Hello, young word explorer.

2
00:00:01.695 --> 00:00:04.237
Welcome to Unit 5, Let's Measure.

3
00:00:04.237 --> 00:00:08.473
This unit has 36 vocabulary cards in 4 learning groups.

4
00:00:08.473 --> 00:00:11.015
Group 1 is Counting in Tens.

5
00:00:11.015 --> 00:00:15.675
Listen for words such as ten, twenty, thirty, forty, fifty, sixty.

6
00:00:15.675 --> 00:00:18.217
Group 2 is Shapes and Patterns.

7
00:00:18.217 --> 00:00:22.878
Listen for words such as circle, square, triangle, rectangle, heart, pattern.

8
00:00:22.878 --> 00:00:24.996
Group 3 is Measuring Words.

9
00:00:24.996 --> 00:00:29.656
Listen for words such as measure, ruler, centimetre, metre, length, height.

10
00:00:29.656 --> 00:00:32.198
Group 4 is Comparing Words (Opposites).

11
00:00:32.198 --> 00:00:36.859
Listen for words such as big, small, long, short, tall, short.

12
00:00:36.859 --> 00:00:47.450
For each word, listen and repeat, read five sentences, notice the word type, practise spelling, write your own sentence, and ask the tutor for help.

13
00:00:47.450 --> 00:00:50.416
You are ready to begin Unit 5.
